                  </span>
                  <span class="inline-flex items-center bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/30 text-green-800 dark:text-green-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-check-circle mr-1 text-xs"></i>
